%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20in%20the%20race%20to%20become%20the%20next%20president%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20hasn't%20made%20significant%20electoral%20gains%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20since%20Mr%20Annamalai%20was%20appointed%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20state%20unit%20in%202021%2C%20the%2040-year-old%20is%20credited%20with%20giving%20it%20much%20more%20visibility%2C%20which%20is%20very%20important%20in%20a%20state%20that%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20nearly%20impenetrable%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20for%20pulling%20no%20punches%2C%20the%20former%20IPS%20officer%2C%20engineer%20and%20MBA%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fiercest%20critics%20of%20the%20ruling%20DMK.%20He%20had%20captured%20the%20national%20spotlight%20when%20he%20flogged%20himself%20six%20times%20in%20December%20last%20year%20to%20mark%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20mega%20protest%20against%20the%20DMK%20after%20a%20student%20of%20Chennai's%20Anna%20University%20was%20raped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnybody%20who%20understands%20Tamil%20culture%20will%20understand%20this.%20Flogging%20ourselves%2C%20%C2%A0punishing%20ourselves%2C%20it%20is%20part%20of%20this%20culture...%20This%20protest%20is%20not%20against%20a%20specific%20person%20or%20thing%2C%20it%20is%20against%20a%20continuous%20injustice%20that%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPunishment%20Or%20Promotion%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20sources%20said%20Mr%20Annamalai%20will%20be%20told%20his%20removal%20will%20not%20be%20a%20punishment%20but%20part%20of%20an%20approach%20to%20expand%20the%20footprint%20of%20the%20party%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20that%20a%20bigger%20role%20for%20him%20in%20the%20party%20or%20the%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20has%20not%20been%20ruled%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Annamalai's%20predecessor%2C%20L%20Murugan%2C%20had%20also%20been%20made%20a%20Un