20whether%20a%20%2417%20cocktail%20is%20worth%20it%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20want%20a%20lychee%20martini%20in%20my%20bloodstream%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20instead%20of%20having%20honest%20discussions%20about%20vacation%20spending%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20just%20avoid%20them.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20we%20planned%20our%20first-ever%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-family-spent-10k-disney-world-trip-tips-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney%20World%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20February%20break%2C%20we%20thought%20we%20had%20cracked%20the%20code%3A%20Go%20all-inclusive.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20booked%20a%20room%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-contemporary-resort-review-for-adults-lake-view-room-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney's%20Contemporary%20Resort%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20opted%20for%20the%20Disney%20Dining%20Plan.%20The%20idea%20was%20that%20if%20everything%20was%20prepaid%2C%20there'd%20be%20no%20decisions%20left%20to%20argue%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2b59cb1-414a-4d04-8116-ce845069c5fe%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoing%20all-inclusive%20quickly%20turned%20us%20into%20theme-park%20economists%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223984%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cinderella's%20Castle%20at%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20in%20Florida.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67368630fa0140cdd563a3e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222656%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBy%20handing%20over%20our%20money%20upfront%20and%20going%20all-in%20on%20extras%2C%20we%20thought%2C%20wouldn't%20have%20to%20think%20about%20spending%20throughout%20our%20Disney%20World%20trip.%3Cp%3EArturo%20Holmes%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Disney%20Dreamers%20Academy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20our%20plan%20totally%20worked!%20We%20tapped%20our%20MagicBands%20without%20a%20second%20thought%20to%20bickering%20over%20%2412%20Mickey-shaped%20pretzels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20our%203-year-old%20had%20a%20full-scale%20meltdown%20at%20Chef%20Mickey's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-world-vs-universal-character-dining-which-is-better-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echaracter%20dinner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20didn't%20feel%20the%20sting%20of%20wasted%20money%20%E2%80%94%20we%20just%20laughed%20and%20accepted%20that%20oversized%20cartoon%20heads%20on%20human%20bodies%20are%2C%20objectively%2C%20the%20stuff%20of%20nightmares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20all-inclusive%20plan%20helped%20us%20avoid%20fights%2C%20it%20also%20unleashed%20something%20unexpected%3A%20the%20unrelenting%20need%20to%20%3Cem%3Emaximize.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20we%20weren't%20just%20skipping%20the%20money%20bickering%20%E2%80%94%20we%20were%20fully%20committed%20to%20extracting%20every%20ounce%20of%20value%20from%20our%20prepaid%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20we%20found%20ourselves%20at%207%20p.m.%2C%20dragging%20two%20very%20sleepy%20children%20back%20into%20Magic%20Kingdom%20because%2C%20dammit%2C%20we%20paid%20for%20those%20full-day%20passes%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20also%20how%20we%20ended%20up%20on%20The%20Little%20Mermaid%20ride%2C%20each%20adult%20cradling%20a%20completely%20unconscious%20child%2C%20whispering%20to%20ourselves%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20magic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20day%20two%2C%20our%20warped%20logic%20had%20fully%20taken%20over.%20Did%20we%20need%20to%20be%20there%20for%20rope-drop%20at%20Epcot%20after%20staying%20out%20late%20for%20the%20Magic%20Kindom%20fireworks%3F%20No.%20But%20we%20%3Cem%3Ecould%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20it%20was%3Cem%3E%20included%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20so%20we%20%3Cem%3Emust.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20very%20thing%20meant%20to%20reduce%20stress%20drove%20us%20into%20full-blown%20vacation%20optimization%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be433224-1d1a-4a76-91fa-c6d3c71b702c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFortunately%2C%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20find%20the%20sweet%20spot%20for%20sanity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224592%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mickey%20mouse%20shaped%20soft%20pretzel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656506b4fe5bc6545ebca7f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESometimes%2C%20it's%20OK%20to%20just%20buy%20the%20pretzel.%3Cp%3EMaciej%20Badetko%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20we%20left%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20both%20relieved%20and%20deeply%20aware%20of%20our%20own%20absurdity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20the%20all-inclusive%20plan%20helped%20us%20avoid%20our%20usual%20debates%20over%20spending%2C%20but%20it%20also%20made%20us%20act%20like%20we%20were%20strategizing%20for%20a%20corporate%20retreat%20rather%20than%20enjoying%20a%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20and%20your%20partner%20approach%20spending%20differently%2C%20especially%20on%20vacations%2C%20here%20are%20a%20few%20things%20I've%20learned%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22287be8fc-c219-4c86-9cc9-6d26b7188a19%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgree%20to%20a%20budget%20ahead%20of%20time%20%E2%80%94%20but%20allow%20some%20flexibility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20book%20anything%2C%20have%20the%20hard%20conversations%20upfront%20and%20decide%20on%20a%20spending%20plan%20together.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20person%20needs%20a%20clear%20budget%20to%20feel%20comfortable%2C%20set%20that%20one%20in%20advance.%20If%20the%20other%20(hi%2C%20it's%20me)%20wants%20some%20spontaneity%2C%20build%20in%20a%20little%20wiggle%20room%20for%20guilt-free%20indulgence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20next%20time%2C%20we'll%20establish%20some%20%26quot%3Bno-questions-asked%26quot%3B%20splurge%20z