A%20Congress%20MP%20challenges%20legality%20of%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%202025%20in%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743765354000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-news-updates-trump-tariffs-manoj-kumar-waqf-bill-jdu-leaders-bihar-chief-minister-nitish-kumar-125040400187_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Latest%20news%20updates%3A%20Catch%20all%20the%20latest%20news%20updates%20from%20around%20the%20world%20here%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-news-updates-trump-tariffs-manoj-kumar-waqf-bill-jdu-leaders-bihar-chief-minister-nitish-kumar-125040400187_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDon't%20Push%20Us%20To%20Wall%26quot%3B%3A%20Omar%20Abdullah's%20Party%20To%20Centre%20Amid%20Transfer%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Omar%20Abdullah-led%20National%20Conference%20today%20passed%20two%20resolutions%2C%20one%20urging%20the%20Centre%20to%20respect%20the%20people's%20mandate%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20another%20condemning%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolutions%20followed%20a%20two-hour%20legislative%20party%20meeting%20of%20the%20ruling%20National%20Conference%20and%20its%20allies.%20They%20come%20amid%20a%20tussle%20between%20the%20Omar%20Abdullah%20government%20and%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha's%20office.%20The%20National%20Conference%20has%20said%20it%20wants%20to%20run%20the%20government%20with%20%26quot%3Blove%20and%20respect%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20silence%20should%20not%20be%20construed%20as%20its%20%26quot%3Bweakness%26quot%3B.%20It%20has%20also%20urged%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20to%20%26quot%3Bnot%20push%20them%20to%20the%20wall%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20first%20major%20confrontation%20between%20the%20Union%20Territory's%20government%20and%20Raj%20Bhavan%20is%20the%20transfer%20of%2048%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Administrative%20Service%20(JKAS)%20officers%20on%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor's%20instructions.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20elected%20government%20feels%20that%20the%20order%20disrespects%20the%20people's%20mandate%20and%20tramples%20upon%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20Omar%20Abdullah%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can't%20be%20business%20as%20usual.%20We%20wanted%20cordial%20relations%20with%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20and%20the%20Centre%2C%20but%20they%20have%20chosen%20to%20disrespect%20the%20mandate.%20It's%20unacceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20National%20Conference%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20National%20Conference%20leader%20told%20the%20media%20that%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20and%20MLAs%20of%20the%20National%20Conference%20and%20its%20allies%20attended%20the%20meeting.%20%26quot%3BWe%20passed%20two%20key%20resolutions.%20One%20strongly%20rejects%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill.%20We%20believe%20it%20is%20against%20the%20Muslims.%20The%20second%20resolution%20is%20that%20the%20mandate%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20people%20must%20be%20respected.%20We%20have%20requested%20the%20government%20to%20respect%20the%20mandate.%20Our%20coordination%20must%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20our%20weakness.%20This%20is%20the%20last%20time%20we%20want%20to%20appeal%2C%20don't%20push%20us%20to%20the%20wall%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20has%20erupted%20days%20ahead%20of%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20visit%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Mr%20Shah%20is%20scheduled%20to%20reach%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%20Sunday%20for%20a%20three-day%20visit%20to%20review%20the%20security%20situation%20amid%20a%20spike%20in%20terrorist%20activities%20in%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20reportedly%20written%20to%20the%20Home%20Minister%2C%20expressing%20his%20resentment%20over%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan's%20transfer%20orders%20and%20pointing%20out%20that%20this%20falls%20within%20the%20domain%20of%20the%20elected%20government%20under%20the%202019%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Act%20authorises%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20to%20transfer%20IAS%20officers%20and%20control%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%20All%20other%20departments%2C%20including%20the%20transfer%20of%20JKAS%20officers%2C%20fall%20under%20the%20elected%20government's%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20because%20he%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20law%20and%20order%2C%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20issued%20the%20order%20transferring%20Revenue%20officers%20because%20they%20also%20perform%20the%20duties%20of%20magistrates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Omar%20Abdullah%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%20October%20last%20year%20after%20a%20thumping%20victory%20in%20the%20Assembly%20election.%20The%20government%20and%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20have%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20tussle%20since%20then%20due%20to%20overlapping%20powers.%20Mr%20Abdullah%20has%20stressed%20that%20he%20wants%20cordial%20ties%20with%20the%20Centre%2C%20but%20the%20recent%20developments%20have%20irked%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20unease%20in%20the%20elected%20government%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20the%20restoration%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20statehood%2C%20which%20it%20lost%20when%20its%20special%20status%20was%20revoked%20in%202019.%20The%20Centre%20had%20reportedly%20assured%20Mr%20Abdullah%20that%20the%20consultation%20on%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20would%20start%20soon%20after%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Maharashtra.%20But%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20refused%20to%20give%20any%20timeline%20for%20these%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743765240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc