%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGranger%2C%20Boyd%2C%20and%20Kynsley%20on%20a%20group%20trip.%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorld%20of%20Travel%26quot%3B%2F%20Gilded%20Focus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGranger%20and%20Boyd%20advise%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-group-tour-changed-my-approach-to-travel-with-kids-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraveling%20with%20a%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20can%20help%20with%20parenting%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20recommend%20traveling%20with%20family%20or%20a%20friend%20who's%20willing%20to%20watch%20the%20baby%20and%20let%20the%20adult%20be%20an%20adult%2C%26quot%3B%20Granger%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20bunch%20of%20family%20and%20friends%20with%20us%20on%20the%20same%20flight%20to%20South%20Africa.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGranger%20added%20that%20having%20so%20many%20loved%20ones%20around%20on%20their%2015-and-a-half-hour%20flight%20to%20South%20Africa%20seemed%20to%20make%203-year-old%20Kynsley%20feel%20more%20comfortable%20on%20the%20plane%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDo%20your%20research%20to%20ensure%20you%20don't%20overpack%20large%20items%20like%20strollers%20or%20car%20seats.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20a%20mother%20holding%20a%20baby%20on%20a%20cobblestone%20street%20and%20a%20baby%20in%20a%20stroller%20next%20to%20her%20father%20at%20the%20airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bde2a2c040bd1b4ca30d99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGranger%20and%20Boyd%20took%20Kynsley%20to%20international%20destinations%20as%20a%20baby%20and%20a%20toddler.%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorld%20of%20Travel%26quot%3B%2F%20Gilded%20Focus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20big%20lessons%20we%20learned%20as%20a%20group%20is%20how%20to%20condense%20and%20pack%20appropriately%20for%20the%20t