es%20for%20a%20new%2020%20per%20cent%20flat%20tariff%20on%20all%20products%20bound%20for%20the%20US%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20hurt%20exports%20of%20alcohol%20and%20luxury%20goods%2C%20among%20other%20things.%20Arnault's%20LVMH%2C%20a%20conglomerate%20which%20owns%20brands%20including%20Christian%20Dior%2C%20Bulgari%20and%20Loro%20Piana%2C%20saw%20its%20shares%20fall%20in%20Paris%2C%20wiping%20%246%20billion%20off%20the%20net%20worth%20of%20Europe's%20richest%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20reserved%20some%20of%20the%20highest%20tariffs%20for%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bnations%20that%20treat%20us%20badly%26quot%3B.%20That%20included%20an%20additional%2034%20per%20cent%20on%20goods%20from%20China%20--%20bringing%20the%20new%20added%20tariff%20rate%20there%20to%2054%20per%20cent.%20The%20figure%20for%20the%20European%20Union%20was%2020%20per%20cent%2C%20and%2024%20per%20cent%20on%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743758700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F7fvc7k7g_elon-musk-mark-zuckerberg-and-jeff-bezos_625x300_12_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbillionaires-lost-208-billion-after-trump-tariff-announcement-biggest-loser-is-8085529%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20drop%20is%20the%20fourth-largest%20one-day%20decline%20in%20the%20Billionaires%20Index's%2013-year%20history%2C%20and%20the%20largest%20since%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbillionaires-lost-208-billion-after-trump-tariff-announcement-biggest-loser-is-8085529%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98There%20will%20be%20blood%E2%80%99%3A%20Is%20the%20world%20staring%20at%20a%20recession%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743758543000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119975387%2Ci