usinessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fwhat-is-hipaa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20criminal%20activity%20and%20wiretaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20more%20people%20with%20government%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20and%20familiarity%20with%20the%20federal%20guidelines%20his%20company%20needs%20to%20adhere%20to%20%E2%80%94%20are%20or%20soon%20could%20be%20out%20of%20work%2C%20Walker%20expects%20it%20will%20be%20easier%20than%20in%20the%20past%20to%20find%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalker%20said%20he's%20hoping%20to%20hire%20as%20many%20as%2010%20transcriptionists%20in%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20months%20for%20various%20contracts%20that%20he%20expects%20will%20come%20through.%20The%20company%20is%20based%20in%20Denver%2C%20but%20most%20of%20its%2050-some%20employees%20work%20remotely%20throughout%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalker%20said%20he%20might%20also%20use%20the%20market's%20surplus%20of%20qualified%20workers%20to%20cut%20a%20handful%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-job-after-fired-work-performance-issues-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-performers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20wouldn't%20we%20replace%20them%20with%20three%20or%20four%20outstanding%20people%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220166e0a4-5a81-4a39-a98c-59116af7942c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'A%20ton%20of%20opportunity'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHassan%20said%20Range%20is%20looking%20to%20hire%20100%20people%2C%20including%20staffers%20in%20operations%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20product%20management%20and%20more%20than%2030%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERange%20is%20largely%20hiring%20at%20its%20McLean%2C%20Virginia%2C%20headquarters%2C%20though%20also%20in%20the%20New%20York%20and%20Seattle%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20ton%20of%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20Hassan%20said.%20Many%20would-be%20employees%20exiting%20the%20government%20he's%20met%20