na%20Cooper%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnna%20Cooper%2C%2032%2C%20worked%20in%20property%20management%20for%20two%20years%20after%20college.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe's%20used%20her%20negotiation%20skills%20to%20bring%20down%20her%20rent%20and%20parking%20fees.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECooper%20shared%20four%20insider%20tips%20to%20successfully%20negotiate%20with%20your%20landlord.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Anna%20Cooper%2C%2032%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20resident%20services%20coordinator.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20Cooper's%20employment%20history.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%202018%20to%202020%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20resident%20services%20coordinator%20for%20a%20luxury%20multi-family%20property%20in%20Washington%20DC%20and%20learned%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20rental%20process%20from%20the%20landlord%20side%20of%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20made%20people%20more%20sensitive%20about%20their%20finances%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20many%20became%20more%20proactive%20about%20negotiating%20their%20rent.%20It%20was%20great%20to%20see%20rent%20negotiations%20firsthand%20because%20before%20then%2C%20I%20didn't%20even%20know%20that%20was%20something%20you%20could%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20since%20moved%20on%20from%20working%20in%20property%20management%2C%20but%20I've%20used%20the%20tips%20I%20learned%20from%20the%20job%20to%20negotiate%20my%20own%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb6d7175-7256-4128-9e98-d328cbb6a2a8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstand%20the%20leverage%20you%20have%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20don't%20think%20they%20have%20the%20option%20to%20negotiate%2C%20but%20you%20can%20definitely%20make%20your%20renting%20experience%20work%20in%20your%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20think%20about%20it%20from%20the%20landlord%20perspective%2C%20it's%20important%20for%20them%20to%20retain%20you%20as%20a%20tenant.%20It's%20really%20expensive%20to%20turn%20a%20unit%20over.%20They%20have%20to%20push%20out%20marketing%20to%20let%20the%20public%20know%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20these%20units%20are%20now%20up%20for%20lease%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20there%20are%20different%20companies%20that%20they%20use%20and%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20to%20put%20a%20unit%20back%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20take%20that%20into%20account%2C%20you%20realize%20you%20can%20negotiate%20to%20stay%20and%20lock%20in%20another%20lease.%20That%20way%2C%20the%20landlord%20doesn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20a%20unit%20sitting%20vacant%20for%20X%20amount%20of%20months%20or%20a%20year%20when%20they%20could%20continue%20to%20bring%20in%20profit%20just%20by%20negotiating%20with%20someone%20to%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2212e4bf09-d165-4767-acab-d8d1c3289b8c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELine%20up%20your%20negotiation%20chips%20early%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20want%20to%20start%20doing%20your%20research%2060%20to%2090%20days%20before%20your%20lease%20renewal%20date.%20If%20you%20start%20thinking%20about%20the%20renewal%20process%20a%20few%20months%20ahead%20of%20time%2C%20you%20can%20get%20a%20better%20idea%20of%20the%20rental%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAre%20there%20better%20properties%20with%20cheaper%20rates%3F%20What's%20my%20experience%20at%20the%20building%20I'm%20in%20right%20now%3F%20Could%20it%20be%20better%3F%20These%20are%20all%20good%20questions%20to%20ask%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20your%20experience%20on%20the%20current%20lease%20because%20these%20could%20become%20negotiating%20chips.%20Maybe%20you've%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20service%20requests%20and%20maintenance%20orders%20for%20things%20that%20are%20no%20fault%20of%20your%20own.%20For%20example%2C%20maybe%20you%20have%20a%20washer%20and%20dryer%20that%20has%20just%20not%20been%20great.%20Maybe%20there's%20a%20new%20building%20across%20the%20street%2C%20but%20you%20were%20told%20you%20would%20be%20living%20across%20from%20an%20empty%20lot%2C%20and%20the%20construction%20has%20impacted%20your%20peace%20of%20mind.%20Keep%20note%20of%20things%20that%20have%20impacted%20your%20quality%20of%20living%2C%20and%20be%20prepared%20to%20bring%20them%20up%20in%20your%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20don't%20often%20consider%20starting%20early.%20They'll%20wait%20for%20a%20letter%20or%20an%20email%20from%20their%20property%20manager%20to%20start%20the%20lease%20renewal%20process%2C%20but%20by%20that%20point%2C%20they've%20lost%20the%20edge%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b60f7ba4-85b6-4592-963e-5780898a8d32%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20be%20discouraged%20by%20a%20'no'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20when%20you%20send%20a%20letter%20or%20email%20to%20your%20landlord%20to%20negotiate%2C%20you%20get%20told%20%26quot%3Bno.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sucks%2C%20but%20if%20that%20happens%2C%20be%20prepared%20to%20ask%20them%20again.%20Check%20to%20see%20if%20there's%20someone%20above%20your%20landlord%2C%20like%20the%20regional%20property%20manager.%20Everyone%20answers%20to%20something%20above%20them%20if%20it's%20a%20larger%20property.%20For%20mom-and-pop%20landlords%2C%20you%20may%20have%20less%20leverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20doesn't%20hurt%20to%20ask%20your%20neighbors%20what%20they're%20paying%20for%20rent%2C%20if%20they%20negotiated%2C%20and%20if%20they've%20experienced%20any%20issues%20living%20in%20the%20building.%20Getting%20more%20information%20can%20help%20you%20negotiate%20with%20your%20landlord%20more%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b2e3e02-467b-46f4-9185-6c13d3e821cf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENegotiate%20different%20amenities%2C%20and%20keep%20a%20paper%20trail%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20moved%20to%20LA%2C%20I%20created%20an%20Excel%20spreadsheet%20of%20all%20of%20the%20properties%20I%20toured.%20I%20tracked%20things%20like%20the%20rent%2C%20the%20square%20footage%20of%20the%20unit%2C%20what%20amenities%20were%20included%2C%20parking%2C%20and%20other%20important%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20went%20on%20these%20tours%2C%20I%20compared%20each%20of%20them%20to%20see%20what%20made%20the%20most%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20some%20properties%20were%20a%20couple%20of%20blocks%20away%20or%20within%20a%20mile%20of%20another%20one%2C%20I%20would%20open%20up%20negotiations%20with%20the%20property%20manager%20and%20say%20something%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20between%20this%20apartment%20and%20another%20one.%20This%20one%20has%20a%20bit%20more%20square%20footage%2C%20but%20this%20one%20here%20is%20charging%20a%20bit%20more%20for%20parking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20signing%20a%20lease%2C%20I%20spoke%20to%20the%20leasing%20agent%20who%20gave%20me%20the%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnytime%20you're%20negotiating%20something%20like%20this%2C%20you%20want%20to%20have%20that%20trail%20in%20writing.%20I%20sent%20a%20follow-up%20email%20to%20the%20leasing%20agent%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20thank%20you%20so%20much%20for%20the%20tour.%20As%20discussed%20earlier%20today%2C%20I%20would%20love%20if%20we%20could%20look%20into%20potential%20options%20for%20a%20longer%20lease%20term%2C%20plus%20a%20parking%20credit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20replied%20back%20to%20the%20email%20saying%20that%20he%20would%20loop%20in%20his%20regional%20manager.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20instead%20of%20signing%20a%2012-month%20lease%20term%2C%20I%20negotiated%20a%2013-month%20lease%20term%20that%20made%20my%20rent%20cheaper%20and%20included%20a%20discounted%20rate%20on%20parking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-tips-to-negotiate-cheaper-rent-landlord-housing-market-affordable-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%