%20and%20venture%20capital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Donald%20Trump%20silhouette%20overlooking%20a%20downward%20arrow%20on%20tech%20gadgets%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673cec5cede4eeae3928791a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESAUL%20LOEB%2FGetty%2C%20Peter%20Stark%2FGetty%2C%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump's%20sweeping%20tariffs%20could%20hit%20tech%20startups%20hard.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EVCs%20expect%20rising%20costs%20and%20fundraising%20struggles%20for%20companies%20relying%20on%20offshore%20operations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20worry%20the%20tariffs%20could%20freeze%20exit%20markets%20as%20companies%20hope%20to%20IPO%20or%20get%20bought.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20long-awaited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-do-trump-tariffs-work-what-are-tariffs-trump-plan-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20arrived%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20US%20markets%20are%20reeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-unveils-reciprocal-tariffs-at-liberation-day-white-house-event-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edebuted%20broad%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20announcing%20a%2010%25%20baseline%20tariff%20on%20all%20countries%2C%20as%20well%20as%20higher%20tariffs%20of%20up%20to%2050%25%20on%20imported%20goods%20from%20specific%20countries.%20The%20Trump%20administration's%20goal%2C%20as%20they%20put%20it%2C%20is%20to%20manage%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20unbalanced%26quot%3B%20trade%20deficits%20and%20bring%20manufacturing%20and%20supply%20chains%20back%20into%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20tariffs%20have%20plenty%20of%20US-based%20investors%20and%20founders%20worried.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index%20fell%20more%20than%204%25%20after%20Trump's%20announcement%2C%20with%20some%20companies'%20individual%20stocks%20tumbling%20far%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20and%20founders%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20tariffs%20could%20have%20significant%20consequences%20for%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20including%20for%20startups%20and%20venture%20capital%20%E2%80%94%20potentially%20raising%20the%20costs%20of%20doing%20business%2C%20stunting%20exit%20opportunities%2C%20and%20forcing%20startups%20to%20further%20tighten%20their%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20ways%20Trump's%20tariff%20policy%20could%20affect%20tech%20workers%20and%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETariffs%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20broader%20market%20correction%20that%20makes%20fundraising%20harder%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trump%20holding%20up%20a%20board%20showing%20reciprocal%20tariffs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eeaaab63d72727e199182d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20President%20Trump%20announced%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%2C%20imposing%20duties%20ranging%20from%2010%25%20to%2049%25%20on%20imports%20from%2060%20trade%20partners.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump's%20trade%20war%20has%20rattled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-correction-trump-tariffs-inflation-ai-stocks-job-market-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estock%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20stoked%20fears%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-trump-tariffs-recession-doge-china-trade-war-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecession%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20has%20some%20in%20tech%20worried%20about%20how%20a%20broader%20market%20correction%20could%20trickle%20down%20to%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20tighter%20economy%20could%20force%20some%20limited%20partners%20to%20call%20off%20investments%20in%20venture%20funds%20as%20the%20value%20of%20their%20public%20assets%20tumbles%20%E2%80%94%20a%20phenomenon%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bdenominator%20effect.%26quot%3B%20This%20would%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20investors%20to%20close%20new%20funds.%20They%20might%20also%20whittle%20down%20the%20target%20size%20of%20their%20funds%2C%20recognizing%20that%20startups%20will%20raise%20smaller%20rounds%20in%20a%20funding%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20tariffs%20stick%2C%20and%20if%20we%20see%20kind%20of%20a%20broader%20market%20correction%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20venture%20going%20the%20same%20way%20it%20has%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20where%20it's%20difficult%20to%20raise%20capital%20and%20to%20manage%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marcos%20Fernandez%2C%20cofounder%20and%20managing%20partner%20of%20Fiat%20Ventures.%20%26quot%3BUnless%20you%20have%20a%20really%20differentiated%20model%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20difficult%20to%20weather%20that%20storm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20IPO%20window%20could%20close%20shortly%20after%20it%20opened%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stock%20Market%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b26262a5247369a3e9d623%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInvestors%20worry%20the%20market's%20volatility%20in%20response%20to%20the%20tariffs%20will%20shrink%20the%20backlog%20of%20companies%20seeking%20to%20go%20public.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20startups%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhinge-healths-ipo-filing-most-important-takeaways-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebegun%20to%20queue%20up%20for%20IPO%20listings%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trump's%20latest%20