manufacturing%20facility%20where%20Apple's%20Mac%20Pros%20are%20assembled%20in%20Austin%2C%20Texas%2C%20on%20November%2020%2C%202019.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eeab7e63d72727e1991857%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrump%20toured%20one%20of%20Apple's%20manufacturing%20facilities%20in%20Texas%20in%202019.%20Most%20of%20Apple's%20products%20are%20manufactured%20in%20China%2C%20which%20will%20put%20the%20tech%20giant%20in%20the%20crosshairs%20of%20Trump's%20tariffs.%3Cp%3EMandel%20Ngan%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20said%20startups%20building%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-tariffs-could-impact-hardware-consumer-goods-startups-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehardware%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20other%20physical%20goods%20could%20be%20especially%20impacted%20by%20Trump's%20new%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHardware%20startups%20rely%20on%20a%20host%20of%20manufacturers%20that%20are%20mostly%20based%20in%20China.%20Those%20Chinese%20manufacturers%20now%20face%20a%2054%25%20total%20effective%20tariff%20on%20goods%20imported%20to%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20a%20combination%20of%20a%2034%25%20Liberation%20Day%20tariff%20imposed%20on%20China%20and%20a%20previous%2020%25%20price%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndreas%20Schwarzenbrunner%2C%20a%20Paris-based%20general%20partner%20at%20Speedinvest%2C%20said%20industries%20that%20depend%20on%20complex%20manufacturing%2C%20such%20as%20electronics%2C%20machinery%2C%20and%20chip%20production%2C%20and%20hardware-dependent%20sectors%20could%20see%20spiking%20costs%20and%20supply%20chain%20disruptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20healthcare%20companies%20could%20feel%20the%20sting%20of%20tariffs%20if%20they%20manufacture%20their%20drugs%20and%20devices%20offshore%2C%20said%20Sunny%20Kumar%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Informed%20Ventures.%20Those%20companies%20%26quot%3Bnow%20have%20to%20decide%20whether%20to%20pass%20on%20these%20new%20costs%20to%20their%20customers%20or%20absorb%20them%20themselves%2C%20given%20the%20significant%20time%20and%20infrastructure%20needed%20to%20onshore%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Overlap%20Holdings'%20Stevens%20maintains%20that%20some%20high-margin%20businesses%20in%20categories%20such%20as%20robotics%2C%20life%20sciences%2C%20or%20space%20may%20more%20easily%20weather%20the%20price%20hikes.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20building%20a%20robot%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20metal%20inputs%20into%20the%20robot%20is%20a%20very%20small%20fraction%20of%20what%20you're%20selling%20that%20robot%20for.%20And%20so%20you%20have%20a%20lot%20more%20profit%20margin%20to%20work%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Stevens%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20growth%20of%20US%20manufacturing%20may%20lead%20to%20rising%20demand%20for%20global%20talent%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DeepSeek%20Logo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679808f3196626c40985374b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChina's%20AI%20market%20is%20booming%20as%20Chinese%20companies%20like%20OpenAI%20rival%20DeepSeek%20and%20TikTok%20parent%20company%20ByteDance%20attract%20and%20cultivate%20AI%20talent.%3Cp%3EDado%20Ruvic%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqz.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-bring-back-jobs-reshore-1851774578%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3BJobs%20and%20factories%20will%20come%20roaring%20back%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20rolled%20out%20sweeping%20tariffs.%20If%20that%20happens%2C%20the%20creation%20of%20new%20jobs%20could%20exacerbate%20an%20already%20stretched%20labor%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tariffs%20may%20also%20deter%20some%20skilled%20foreign%20workers%20from%20bringing%20their%20talents%20onshore%2C%20said%20Krish%20Ramadurai%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20AIX%20Ventures%2C%20which%20invests%20in%20the%20software%20and%20biotech%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTariffs%20signal%20a%20closed-door%20stance%20that%20repels%20global%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20US%20innovation%20edge%20depends%20on%20openness%2C%20and%20losing%20that%20could%20prove%20more%20costly%20long-term%20than%20any%20tariff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20manufacturing%20revival%20could%20also%20lead%20companies%20to%20seek%20out%20top%20global%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESophie%20Alcorn%2C%20a%20business%20immigration%20attorney%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-tech-immigration-policy-donald-trump-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvises%20tech%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20startups%2C%20predicts%20that%20the%20construction%20of%20state-of-the-art%20factories%2C%20such%20as%20Apple's%20new%20Houston%20digs%20and%20Hyundai's%20Georgia%20plant%2C%20will%20actually%20create%20job%20opportunities%20for%20high-skilled%20immigrant%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20technicality%20of%20some%20of%20these%20advanced%20manufacturing%20processes%20is%20going%20to%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20brilliant%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20Alcorn%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20certainly%20need%20to%20rely%20on%20brilliant%20people%20from%20around%20the%20world%20to%20help%20us%20build%20them%20in%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECompanies%20may%20face%20a%20pricing%20conundrum%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Restoration%20hardware%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c069ba8bde70f2f3b1e3a60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222041%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFurniture%20seller%20Restoration%20Hardware%20saw%20its%20stock%20tumble%20more%20than%2040%25%20following%20news%20of%20the%20tariffs%20coupled%20with%20the%20company's%20subpar%20earnings%20report.%3Cp%3EAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20now%20face%20a%20difficult%20choice%3A%20absorb%20the%20increased%20costs%20or%20raise%20prices%20for%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20that%20are%20best%20positioned%20to%20pass%20rising%20costs%20onto%20customers%20are%20those%20making%20and%20selling%20%26quot%3Bmission-critical%26quot%3B%20products%2C%20said%20Tusk%20Venture%20Partners'%20Nof.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20providing%20a%20mission-critical%20product%20to%20anyone%20that's%20a%20must-have%20rather%20than%20a%20nice-to-have%20%E2%80%94%20groceries%2C%20medications%2C%20shelter%2C%20things%20you%20have%20to%20have%20to%20survive%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20going%20to%20buy%20that%20regardless%2C%20so%20you'll%20be%20more%20willing%20to%20take%20an%20incremental%20increase%20in%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20Nof%20said.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20else%20starts%20to%20get%20cut.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20is%20true%20for%20business%20software.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20going%20to%20stop%20buying%20software%20altogether%2C%26quot%3B%20Nof%20said%2C%20but%20enterprises%20will%20become%20more%20discerning%20about%20the%20subscriptions%20they%20keep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-tech-trends-trump-trade-war-startups-vc-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743757261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673cec5cede4eeae3928791a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-tech-trends-trump-trade-war-startups-vc-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Investors%20are%20telling%20startups%20to%20batten%20down%20the%20hatches%20after%20Trump's%20latest%20tariffs%20to%20counteract%20potential%20cost%20hikes%20and%20funding%20freezes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rtorrence%40businessinsider.com%20(Rebecca%20Torrence%2CMelia%20Russell%2CJulia%20Hornstein%2CVishal%20Persaud%2CRiddhi%20Kanetkar)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-tech-trends-trump-trade-war-startups-vc-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20startup%20is%20reviving%20a%20Cold%20War-era%20'sea%20monster'%20glider%20for%20modern%20logistics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Poseidon%20Aerospace's%20Seagull%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ef0085b8b41a9673fc9d58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221728%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPoseidon%20Aerospace%20is%20building%20an%20uncrewed%20sea%20glider%20called%20the%20Seagull.%3Cp%3EPoseidon%20Aerospace%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPoseidon%20Aerospace%20emerges%20from%20stealth%20with%20its%20uncrewed%20seal%20glider%20dubbed%20the%20Seagull.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInspired%20by%20the%20Soviet%20Caspian%20Sea%20Monster%2C%20Seagull%20uses%20low-altitude%20flight%20to%20reduce%20drag.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPoseidon%20plans%20to%20test%20the%20Seagull%20with%20the%20US%20Navy%20and%20Coast%20Guard%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20startups%2C%20Poseidon%20Aerospace%20began%20with%20a%20niche%20obsession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20friends-turned-cofounders%20David%20Zagaynov%2C%20Parker%20Tenney%2C%20and%20Isaac%20Baumstark%2C%20that%20fixation%20was%20the%20ekranoplan%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Soviet%20hybrid%20boat-plane%20developed%20during%20the%20Cold%20War-era%20that%20skimmed%20just%20above%20the%20water.%20The%20experimental%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-m88-hercules-recovery-vehicle-sank-lithuania-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilitary%20vehicle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20dubbed%20the%20Caspian%20Sea%20Monster%2C%20hasn't%20operated%20since%20the%201980s.%20Still%2C%20its%20core%20principle%20%E2%80%94%20flying%20low%20over%20the%20sea%20to%20reduce%20drag%20and%20increase%20lift%20%E2%80%94%20stuck%20with%20the%20trio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20thought%20that%20this%20is%20incredible%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Zagaynov%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BLike%2C%20why%20isn't%20it%20around%20right%20now%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20cofounder%20trio%20sensed%20an%20opportunity%20to%20apply%20this%20underlying%20tech%20to%20another%20interest%20of%20theirs%20%E2%80%94%20cargo%20transportation%20and%20logistics.%20Within%20a%20year%2C%20it%20raised%20a%20%241.4%20million%20pre-seed%20round%20led%20by%20Starship%20Ventures%20with%20participation%20from%20the%20Draper%20Startup%20House.%20And%20the%20company%20is%20currently%20hiring%20aerospace%2C%20mechanical%2C%20and%20composite%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20San%20Francisco-based%20startup%20emerged%20from%20stealth%20this%20week%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FDavidZagaynov%2Fstatus%2F1906756217395171771%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20showcasing%20its%20first%20operational%20vehicle%2C%20Seagull%2C%20an%20unmanned%2C%20carbon%20fiber%20sea%20glider.%20Given%20its%20ties%20to%20the%20Caspian%20Sea%20Monster%2C%20Sean%20Hoge%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20general%20partner%20of%20Starship%20Ventures%2C%20classifies%20Poseidon%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Brenaissance%20technology%26quot%3B%20company%20%26quot%3Bbuilding%20a%20technology%20that%20has%20previously%20been%20conceptualized%20or%20attempted%20at%20some%20other%20point%20in%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20to%20BI%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoseidon's%20Seagull%2C%20like%20the%20Soviet-era%20vehicle%2C%20flies%20a%20few%20meters%20above%20the%20water.%20Pressurized%20air%20close%20to%20the%20water's%20surface%20reduces%20drag%20and%20increases%20lift%2C%20allowing%20the%20sea%20glider%20to%20carry%20more%20weight%20while%20using%20less%20fuel%2C%20Zagaynov%20said.%20With%20a%2013-foot%20wingspan%2C%20the%20Seagull%20can%20carry%20about%20100%20pounds%2C%20making%20it%20suited%20for%20transporting%20high-priority%20goods%20like%20medical%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20five-person%20company%20also%20hopes%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Defense%20Department%20on%20a%20range%20of%20use%20cases%2C%20Zagaynov%20said.%20It%20will%20also%20begin%20testing%20with%20the%20US%20Navy%20and%20Coast%20Guard%20this%20summer%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FDavidZagaynov%2Fstatus%2F1906756219416850552%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Seagull%20is%20built%20with%20modern%20materials%20like%20carbon%20fiber%20and%20aerospace-grade%20composites%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20lighter%20and%20more%20durable%20than%20its%20Soviet%20predecessor.%20Instead%20of%20having%20a%20crew%20on%20board%2C%20the%20Seagull%20is%20operated%20autonomously%20by%20a%20modified%20version%20of%20two%20open-source%20autopilot%20systems%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bindustry%20standard%20for%20medium-%20to%20small-scale%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20Zagaynov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20it%20is%20uncrewed%2C%20the%20Seagull%20doesn't%20contain%20a%20cockpit%20or%20life%20support%20systems%2C%20making%20it%20cheaper%20and%20easier%20to%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoseidon%20is%20also%20working%20on%20a%20larger%20model%2C%20the%20Heron%2C%20which%20will%20have%20a%2050-foot%20wingspan%20and%20a%20two-ton%20payload%20capacity%20for%20cargo%20and%20contested%20logistics%20missions%2C%20according%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.poseidonaero.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20team%20designs%20and%20manufactures%20the%20vehicles%20from%20its%2015%2C000-square%20foot%20office%20in%20the%20Dog%20Patch%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20appropriately%20once%20a%20shipbuilding%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20startups%20have%20also%20taken%20a%20crack%20at%20rebuilding%20something%20akin%20to%20the%20Caspian%20Sea%20Monster.%20Regent%2C%20a%20Founders%20Fund-backed%20startup%20based%20in%20Rhode%20Island%2C%20makes%20a%20large-scale%20sea%20glider%20that%20aims%20to%20replace%20ferries%20and%20short-haul%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227728%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Posiedon%20Aerospace%20founders%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ef04ea69253ccddf9b36ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPoseidon%20Aerospace%20founders%20Parker%20Tenney%2C%20David%20Zagaynov%2C%20and%20Isaac%20Baumstark.%3Cp%3EPoseidon%20Aerospace%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EZagaynov%20caught%20the%20startup%20bug%20the%20way%20many%20of%20his%20peers%20did%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20high%20school%2C%20I%20watched%20the%20HBO%20show%20%3Cem%3ESilicon%20Valley%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20that%20was%20incredibly%20inspirational%2C%26quot%3B%20Zagaynov%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20oh%2C%20this%20is%20the%20craziest%20world%20ever.%20This%20is%20what%20I%20want%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20father%2C%20an%20immigrant%20who%20started%20his%20own%20software%20engineering%20firm%2C%20also%20imbued%20Zagaynov%20with%20an%20entrepreneurial%20spirit.%20Zagaynov%20went%20to%20UC%20Berkeley%2C%20where%20he%20studied%20computer%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20Amazon%20for%20a%20year%20and%20met%20his%20cofounders%20through%20mutual%20friends.%20Before%20cofounding%20Posiedon%2C%20Tenney%20studied%20mechanical%20engineering%20at%20Cal%20Poly%20and%20worked%20at%20Lockheed%20Martin.%20Baumstark%20learned%20about%20entrepreneurship%20at%20a%20young%20age%20from%20his%20great-grandfather%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Curtiss%20Candy%20Company%2C%20which%20made%20Butterfingers%2C%20and%20became%20interested%20in%20aerospace%20and%20hardware%20companies%20wh