nneera%20Maheena%2C%20MLA%20AS%20Ponnanna%2C%20and%20others%20of%20harassment%20and%20false%20implication%20in%20a%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinay%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Somwarpet%20in%20Karnataka's%20Kodagu%20district%2C%20was%20an%20administrator%20of%20the%20WhatsApp%20group%20%26quot%3BKodagina%20Samasyegalu%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20a%20controversial%20post%20against%20Congress%20MLA%20and%20legal%20advisor%20to%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20AS%20Ponnanna%2C%20had%20been%20shared.%20The%20post%20contained%20an%20edited%20image%20of%20Mr%20Ponnanna%20in%20traditional%20Kodava%20attire%20alongside%20a%20toilet%2C%20accompanied%20by%20derogatory%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%20against%20the%20person%20who%20posted%20the%20image%20and%20the%20admins%20of%20the%20group%2C%20including%20Vinay%2C%20who%20was%20named%20Accused%20No.%203.%20He%20was%20arrested%20and%20later%20released%20on%20bail.%20Despite%20securing%20a%20court%20stay%20on%20the%20case%2C%20Vinay%20alleged%20continued%20harassment%20from%20the%20police%20and%20political%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20past%20two%20months%2C%20I%20have%20not%20been%20in%20control%20of%20my%20mind.%20One%20person%20posted%20a%20WhatsApp%20message%20in%20the%20'Kodagu%20Problems%20and%20Suggestions'%20WhatsApp%20group.%20I%2C%20who%20was%20made%20an%20admin%20just%20five%20days%20before%2C%20was%20held%20responsible%20for%20it.%20A%20politically%20motivated%20FIR%20was%20filed%20against%20me%2C%20and%20I%20was%20labeled%20a%20miscreant%20in%20society.%20Tenneera%20Maheena%2C%20who%20played%20with%20my%20life%20out%20of%20political%20hatred%2C%20is%20directly%20responsible%20for%20my%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20Vinay%20wrote%20in%20his%20suicide%20letter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinay%20feared%20that%20authorities%20intended%20to%20label%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Browdy-sheeter%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20on%20BJP%20leaders%20to%20support%20his%20family%20financially.%20He%20urged%20authorities%20to%20stop%20politically%20motivated%20FIRs%2C%20stating%20that%20his%20death%20should%20serve%20as%20a%20lesson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTenneera%20Maheena%20is%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20all%20this.%20Politically%20motivated%20individuals%20are%20sharing%20his%20article%20on%20social%20media%20and%20defaming%20us%2C%20even%20after%20the%20High%20Court%20granted%20bail%20and%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20FIR.%20How%20fair%20is%20it%20to%20keep%20calling%20us%20criminals%20even%20after%20that%3F%20I've%20heard%20from%20some%20sources%20that%20there's%20even%20a%20plan%20to%20open%20a%20rowdy%20sheet%20on%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20ended%20with%20Vinay%20asking%20for%20forgiveness%20and%20urged%20the%20Karnataka%20BJP%20unit%20to%20help%20his%20mother%2C%20wife%20and%20daughter%20%26quot%3Bsocially%20and%20financially%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20might%20wonder%20why%20this%20is%20happening%20after%20so%20many%20days%20since%20the%20incident.%20I%20was%20waiting%20to%20go%20home%20and%20see%20everyone%20one%20last%20time.%20I%20am%20bidding%20farewell%20with%20the%20sweet%20memories%20I%20have%20with%20my%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20has%20promised%20a%20DCP-level%20probe%20into%20the%20matter.%20Further%20investigations%20into%20the%20case%20are%20underway.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%