3EThe%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20yesterday%20cancelled%20the%20appointments%20of%20all%2025%2C753%20teachers%20and%20other%20staff%20appointed%20by%20the%20West%20Bengal%20School%20Service%20Commission%20in%202016%20for%20massive%20irregularities.%20%26quot%3BIn%20our%20opinion%2C%20this%20is%20a%20case%20wherein%20the%20entire%20selection%20process%20has%20been%20vitiated%20and%20tainted%20beyond%20resolution.%20Manipulations%20and%20frauds%20on%20a%20large%20scale%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20attempted%20cover-up%2C%20have%20dented%20the%20selection%20process%20beyond%20repair%20and%20partial%20redemption.%20The%20credibility%20and%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20selection%20are%20denuded%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20while%20the%20untainted%20candidates%2C%20whose%20names%20did%20not%20come%20up%20during%20the%20investigation%2C%20need%20not%20return%20the%20salaries%20they%20received%20in%20the%20last%20eight%20years%2C%20they%20would%20no%20longer%20have%20their%20jobs.%20The%20court%20has%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20repeat%20the%20selection%20process%20within%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Roychowdhury%20held%20the%20state%20government%20responsible%20for%20what%20they%20are%20going%20through.%20Asked%20if%20he%20expects%20any%20help%20from%20the%20state%20government%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20government%20engineered%20this%20scam.%20What%20can%20we%20expect%20from%20them%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Ranjan%20Bhuyan%20taught%20physical%20science%20to%20students%20of%20Class%209%20and%2010.%20He%20doesn't%20have%20a%20job%20anymore.%20%26quot%3BWe%20studied%2C%20cracked%20a%20competitive%20exam%20and%20got%20a%20job.%20Some%20people%20resorted%20to%20corruption.%20It%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20without%20the%20state%20government's%20support.%20But%20those%20untainted%20like%20us%20were%20expecting%20that%20we%20would%20be%20able%20to%20continue%20in%20our%20jobs.%20This%20judgment%20has%20destroyed%20our%20lives.%20I%20have%20a%20nine-year-old%20daughter%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20my%20mother.%20There%20are%20EMIs%2C%20how%20will%20we%20look%20for%20new%20jobs%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhuyan%20said%20the%20state%20government%20cannot%20escape%20responsibility%20for%20the%20damage%20they%20have%20done.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20so%20much%20corruption%3F%20The%20state%20government%20is%20responsible.%20But%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20should%20have%20given%20relief%20to%20those%20not%20involved%20in%20corruption.%20Why%20did%20I%20lose%20my%20job%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sacked%20teacher%20said%20the%20road%20ahead%20is%20very%20tough.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%2025-26%2C%20I%20would%20have%20cracked%20another%20exam.%20The%20confidence%20levels%20are%20different%20then.%20I%20am%2039%20now%2C%20which%20job%20will%20I%20be%20eligible%20for%3F%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20we%20can%20take%20the%20same%20exam%20in%20three%20months.%20Is%20it%20possible%20to%20crack%20the%20same%20competitive%20exam%20after%2010%20years%3F%20I%20do%20not%20know%20whether%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to.%20The%20judgment%20gave%20the%20same%20punishment%20to%20those%20involved%20in%20corruption%20and%20those%20not%20involved.%20I%20have%20been%20honest%20all%20my%20life%2C%20and%20my%20academics%20are%20good.%20This%20is%20unfair%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20vs%20Trinamool%20Over%20Teachers'%20Sackings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20verdict%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20alleged%20that%20opposition%20parties%20BJP%20and%20CPM%20had%20conspired%20to%20effect%20a%20collapse%20of%20Bengal's%20education%20system.%20She%20also%20said%20she%20cannot%20accept%20the%20verdict%20personally%2C%20even%20though%20her%20government%20would%20implement%20it.%20The%20BJP%20has%20hit%20back%2C%20with%20party%20MP%20Sambit%20Patra%20alleging%20that%20lakhs%20of%20people%20are%20paying%20for%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government's%20corruption.%20%26quot%3BWhere%20is%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20now%3F%20Where%20are%20INDI%20alliance%20partners%3F%20Didi%20will%20go%20to%20jail%2C%20surely%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743749880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F8q52j98g_bengal-teachers_625x300_04_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-teachers-job-case-emis-schoolgoing-children-sacked-bengal-teachers-brace-for-tough-times-8084091%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20cancelling%20the%20appointment%20of%20more%20than%2025%2C000%20teachers%20and%20other%20school%20staff%20in%20West%20Bengal%20has%20sparked%20a%20massive%20political%20row%2C%20with%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20Opposition%20BJP%20and%20CPM%20trading%20barbs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-teachers-job-case-emis-schoolgoing-children-sacked-bengal-teachers-brace-for-tough-times-8084091%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22iPhone's%20Photos%20app%20gets%20new%20features%20with%20iOS%2018.4%20update%3A%20What's%20new%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743749796000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fiphone-s-photos-app-gets-new-features-with-ios-18-4-update-what-s-new-125040400467_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20addition%20to%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%2C%20the%20iOS%2018.4%20update%20has%20added%20new%20features%20to%20the%20iPhone's%20Photos%20app%2C%20such%20as%20new%20sorting%20options%2C%20categories%2C%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fiphone-s-photos-app-gets-new-features-with-ios-18-4-update-what-s-new-125040400467_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20Meets%20Bangladesh's%20M%20Yunus%20For%20The%20First%20Time%20Since%20Regime%20Change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Muhammad%20Yunus%2C%20chief%20advisor%20of%20Bangladesh's%20interim%20government%2C%20met%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BIMSTEC%20Summit%20in%20Bangkok%20today.%C2%A0External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20were%20also%20present.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20meeting%20between%20the%20two%20leaders%20since%20Nobel%20laureate%20Yunus%20took%20charge%20of%20Bangladesh%20following%20the%20ouster%20of%20the%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20government%20in%20August%20last%20year.%20The%20meeting%20assumes%20significance%20amid%20Dhaka's%20growing%20closeness%20with%20Beijing%2C%20a%20development%20Delhi%20has%20been%20watching%20closely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20Delhi%20and%20Dhaka%20have%20taken%20a%20frosty%20turn%20since%20the%20Sheikh%20Hasina-led%20Awami%20League%20government%20was%20overthrown%20after%20a%20nationwide%20movement%20and%20an%20interim%20government%20took%20over.%20The%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20fled%20to%20India.%20In%20the%20months%20following%20the%20change%20of%20guard%2C%20India%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20reports%20of%20attacks%20on%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh.%20Dhaka%20has%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3BBangladesh's%20minorities%20are%20Bangladesh's%20issue%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yunus'%20recent%20remarks%20on%20the%20Northeastern%20states%20in%20India%20stoked%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20drew%20strong%20responses%20from%20the%20region's%20leaders.%20A%20video%20of%20Mr%20Yunus's%20remarks%2C%20apparently%20made%20during%20his%20four-day%20trip%20to%20China%2C%20shows%20him%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20seven%20states%20of%20India%2C%20the%20eastern%20part%20of%20India%2C%20are%20called%20the%20seven%20sisters.%20They%20are%20a%20landlocked%20region%20of%20India.%20They%20have%20no%20way%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20ocean.%26quot%3B%20He%20says%20Bangladesh%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bguardian%20of%20the%20ocean%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20region.%20%26quot%3BThis%20opens%20up%20a%20huge%20possibility.%20This%20could%20be%20an%20extension%20for%20the%20Chinese%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20remarks%2C%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20said%20what%20the%20Bangladesh%20leader%20had%20said%20was%20%26quot%3Boffensive%26quot%3B.%20He%20stressed%20the%20need%20to%20develop%20more%20robust%20rail%20and%20road%20networks%20connecting%20the%20Northeast%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20statement%20made%20by%20Md%20Younis%20of%20Bangladesh%20so%20called%20interim%20Government%20referring%20to%20the%20seven%20sister%20states%20of%20Northeast%20India%20as%20landlocked%20and%20positioning%20Bangladesh%20as%20their%20guardian%20of%20ocean%20access%2C%20is%20offensive%20and%20strongly%20condemnable.%20This%20remark%20underscores%20the%20persistent%20vulnerability%20narrative%20associated%20with%20India's%20strategic%20'Chicken's%20Neck'%20corridor.%26quot%3B%20The%20Chicken's%20Neck%20Corridor%20is%20a%20stretch%20of%20land%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Siliguri%20which%20connects%20the%20region%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20India.%20Nepal%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Bhutan%20surround%20this%20stretch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistorically%2C%20even%20internal%20elements%20within%20India%20have%20dangerously%20suggested%20severing%20this%20critical%20passageway%20to%20isolate%20the%20Northeast%20from%20the%20mainland%20physically.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20to%20develop%20more%20robust%20railway%20and%20road%20networks%20both%20underneath%20and%20around%20the%20Chicken's%20Neck%20corridor.%20Additionally%2C%20exploring%20alternative%20road%20routes%20connecting%20the%20Northeast%20to%20mainland%20India%2C%20effectively%20bypassing%20the%20Chicken's%20Neck%2C%20should%20be%20prioritised%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20this%20may%20pose%20significant%20engineering%20challenges%2C%20it%20is%20achievable%20with%20determination%20and%20innovation.%20Such%20provocative%20statements%20by%20Md%20Younis%20must%20not%20be%20taken%20lightly%2C%20as%20they%20reflect%20deeper%20strategic%20considerations%20and%20longstanding%20agendas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20wrote%20to%20Mr%20Yunus%20on%20March%2026%2C%20wishing%20Bangladesh%20on%20its%20independence%20day.%20In%20his%20letter%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20highlighted%20the%20significance%20of%20mutual%20sensitivity%20and%20said%20the%20Bangladesh%20Liberation%20War%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bshared%20history%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20%26quot%3BWe%20remain%20committed%20to%20advancing%20this%20partnership%2C%20driven%20by%20our%20common%20aspirations%20for%20peace%2C%20stability%2C%20and%20prosperity%2C%20and%20based%20on%20mutual%20sensitivity%20to%20each%20other's%20interests%20and%20concerns%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743749580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F5kf8m8b8_pm-modi-muhammad-yunus-_650x400_04_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-meets-bangladeshs-muhammad-yunus-amid-row-over-northeast-remarks-8084133%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Muhammad%20Yunus%2C%20chief%20advisor%20of%20Bangladesh's%20interim%20government%2C%20are%20meeting%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BIMSTEC%20Summit%20in%20Bangkok