gure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriven%20by%20the%20desire%20to%20create%20a%20clean%20and%20nutritious%20product%2C%20the%20IT%20professional%20made%20the%20daring%20decision%20to%20leave%20her%20stable%20job%20and%20focus%20on%20launching%20her%20own%20business.%20After%20a%20year%20of%20research%2C%20she%20finally%20launched%20Jogurt%20in%20May%202023%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20yoghurt%20that%20people%20with%20PCOS%2C%20like%20myself%2C%20or%20any%20other%20health%20problems%2C%20could%20trust%2C%20one%20that%20was%20free%20of%20preservatives%20or%20added%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20conducted%20extensive%20research%20online%2C%20consulted%20with%20nutritionists%2C%20and%20visited%20the%20farm%20where%20she%20sources%20her%20milk%20to%20carefully%20choose%20the%20best%20ingredients.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20A2%20milk%20in%20the%20Greek%20yogurt%20contributes%20to%20its%20high%20protein%20content%20after%20double%20straining%20and%20is%20easier%20to%20digest%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20science%20behind%20A2%20milk%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Samrakshini%20G%2C%20a%20gynaecologist%20and%20fertility%20specialist%20based%20in%20Bengaluru%20with%2010%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20ongoing%20debate%20surrounding%20the%20type%20of%20milk%20we%20consume.%20She%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CMilk%20is%20classified%20into%20two%20types%2C%20A1%20and%20A2%2C%20distinguished%20by%20a%20single%20protein%20known%20as%20beta-casein.%20The%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20lies%20in%20a%20variation%20of%20just%20one%20amino%20acid.%E2%80%9D%20In%20A1%20milk%2C%20the%20amino%20acid%20at%20position%2067%20is%20histidine%2C%20while%20in%20A2%20milk%2C%20it%20is%20proline.%20This%20seemingly%20small%20difference%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20digestion%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC9393-1_11zon-1743132614-500x750.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jogurt%20contains%20monk%20fruit%20instead%20of%20sugar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC9393-1_11zon-1743132614-500x750.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC9393-1_11zon-1743132614-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC9393-1_11zon-1743132614-768x1152.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC9393-1_11zon-1743132614-1024x1536.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC9393-1_11zon-1743132614-1366x2048.jpg%201366w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC9393-1_11zon-1743132614-1200x1800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC9393-1_11zon-1743132614-150x225.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-416454%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJogurt%20contains%20monk%20fruit%20instead%20of%20sugar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20elaborates%2C%20%E2%80%9CA1%20milk%20produces%20a%20peptide%20called%20beta-casomorphin%207%20(BCM-7)%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20bloating%20and%20stomach%20discomfort.%20In%20contrast%2C%20A2%20milk%20does%20not%20produce%20this%20peptide%2C%20meaning%20it%20typically%20causes%20fewer%20digestive%20issues.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20clarify%20that%20A2%20milk%20is%20not%20lactose-free%2C%20so%20it%20is%20not%20suitable%20for%20individuals%20who%20have%20severe%20lactose%20intolerance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20health%20implications%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSome%20studies%20suggest%20that%20A1%20milk%20could%20be%20linked%20to%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease%20and%20autoimmune%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F322755%2Fkarnataka-divaa-uthkarsha-project-surya-type-one-diabetes-awareness-for-underprivileged-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EType%201%20diabetes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20findings%2C%20however%2C%20are%20based%20on%20observational%20studies%2C%20and%20more%20research%20is%20needed%20to%20draw%20definitive%20conclusions.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20current%20evidence%20suggests%20that%20A2%20milk%20is%20less%20likely%20to%20cause%20gastrointestinal%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20expert%2C%20Dr%20Pronobesh%2C%20an%20obstetrician%20and%20gynaecologist%20based%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CA2%20milk%20is%20a%20superior%20choice%20for%20gut%20health%20because%20the%20A2%20beta-casein%20is%20gentler%20on%20the%20digestive%20system.%20It%20reduces%20discomfort%20like%20bloating%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20inflammation%20in%20people%20who%20can%E2%80%99t%20tolerate%20normal%20milk.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20farm%20(Deep%20Roots%20Farms%20in%20Indore)%20where%20I%20get%20my%20A2%20milk%20feeds%20organic%20produce%20to%20their%20Gir%20cows%2C%20ensuring%20it%E2%80%99s%20safe.%20The%20cows%20are%20not%20hormonally%20altered%20to%20produce%20more%20milk%20and%20are%20treated%20with%20the%20utmost%20care%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20fresh%20A2%20milk%20to%20perfect%20yoghurt%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20making%20Jogurt%20is%20both%20intricate%20and%20time-consuming.%20The%20process%20begins%20by%20sourcing%20fresh%20A2%20milk%2C%20which%20is%20pasteurised.%20It%20is%20a%20process%20of%20heat